COPY public.changelog_entry (id, version, release_date, category, title, description, sort_order) FROM stdin;
11	1.1.49	2026-03-19	Fix	is_valid() blocked all forms	Removed set_expected_value() from Forms::new(). CSRF is already validated upstream in Prisme — the double validation was invalidating every submission even with correct data.	1
6	1.1.50	2026-03-20	Fix	FileField — restriction validation	Invalid files are deleted from disk if validation fails. Submissions without a file no longer create orphan files. upload_to() applies the exact path; the move only happens in finalize() if validation passes.	1
7	1.1.50	2026-03-20	Feature	derive_form — file() option	Models can declare a file field in the DSL: image: String [file(image, "media/uploads")]. Available types: image, document, any.	2
8	1.1.50	2026-03-20	Added	RuniqueForm::clear() + Forms::clear_values()	Clears all field values (except CSRF) and resets submitted to false. Requires &mut self — callable from a handler or from save(&mut self).	3
9	1.1.50	2026-03-20	Fix	Upload form — browser dialog (PRG)	The handler now always redirects after each POST. Removes the "Do you want to resubmit?" browser dialog on page reload.	4
12	1.1.49	2026-03-19	Fix	Makemigrations — FK order and updated_at	New tables are topologically sorted before generation. updated_at generates ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP (MySQL) or a trigger (PostgreSQL). The diff detects columns that gained or lost DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP.	2
14	1.1.51	20/03/2026	Fix	derive_form version → Runique	The publish order was reversed, publishing runique 1.1.50 with the wrong derive_form version 1.1.33 instead of 1.1.34.	4
21	1.1.53	2026/03/21 -> upcoming	Fix	Admin template override	Restore template override via the admin builder, and separate the demo logic.	4
15	1.1.53	2026/03/21	Added	Session invalidation	The ability to make a session unique will be available via the middleware builder, disabled by default.	3
17	1.1.53	2026/03/21	Added	Admin view role	Adding access permissions in the admin view is functional; the documentation will detail it further.	4
16	1.1.53	2026/03/21	Fix	Password	The password field is removed from the admin edit view. Password changes will be handled via a dedicated email-based reset form.	2
13	1.1.53	2026/03/21	Fix	Boolean field	An unchecked boolean field is now treated as false rather than absent — the required validator no longer requires the box to be checked.	1
18	1.1.53	2026/03/21 -> upcoming	Added	CSS versioning	CSS versioning based on a 4-digit token stored in a LazyLock at each rebuild.	1
19	1.1.53	2026/03/21 -> upcoming	Added	Pagination	Pagination via the builder is functional in the local demo.	2
20	1.1.53	2026/03/21 -> upcoming	Fix	trim	Passwords and other database inputs are natively trimmed, preventing any input mismatch caused by accidental whitespace.	3
\.
